<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-30-1197 </DOCNO><TEXT>The Syllabus Information Depiction System (SIDS) is an automated tooldesigned to track the aircrew training syllabi of the Marine Corps. Thisreport is the User's Manual for this data base system, providing userswith instructions to help them use the system more efficiently. Thisdocument contains printed screen layouts that will guide the user step-by-stepthrough the written instructions.</TEXT></DOC>